ll be\nimportant for the use of voids in observational cosmology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2015 11:54:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2015 09:17:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-07"}
